summary: Completely removes four of the least attractive small dead shrub/thicket models for players with low fps trying to improve performance. NOT COMPATIBLE WITH HEARTHFIRE.
descriptionHtml:
[font=\"Palatino Linotype\"]
[color=#FFFF00][size=3][B]DESCRIPTION[/B][/size][/color]

NOT COMPATIBLE WITH HEARTHFIRE

This mod completely removes four models from Skyrim, a Dead Shrub and a Thicket (plus their snow covered versions) to help players with lower end systems get higher fps in external areas.

See pictures for example, but the models I\'m talking about are the wiry looking small branchy plants! The actual item names are:

TreeDeadShrub
TreeDeadShrubSnow
TreeThicket01
TreeThicket01Snow

These are used throughout Skyrim (there are literally tens of thousands of them) and while they do add to visual appeal, they are not critical and are some of the least \"attractive\" fauna, and so if you\'re having low fps issues in exterior areas, this will make at least a small improvement in fps without removing anything too critical or beautiful.

(Made by request for ObliviousParticle)




[color=#FFFF00][size=3][B]INSTALL[/B][/size][/color]

Either use Nexus Mod Manager or download the zip file manually and extract all of its contents to the Skyrim \"Data\" directory.[/font]
